  "text": "Our initial EOG [CITATION_1] results suggested that dysfunction of the RPE may be a characteristic feature of individuals with NF-1. In order to verify our preliminary findings we performed the EOG examination in a two-fold larger group of patients diagnosed with NF-1.",
